Grand Duchy of Ashenmarch
Overview
The Grand Duchy of Ashenmarch is one of the two Grand Duchies that directly border demonic territory. It is a harsh, militarized region known for its barren badlands, constant demonic incursions, and war-focused economy.

Ruler: Grand Duke Ragnar Ashenfist (Age 52, battle-hardened and ruthless)
Capital: Fort Ashen (Population: 105,000)
Total Population: 6.8 million
Economic Condition: Poor – Almost entirely a war economy. Heavy conscription and high taxes.

Geography & Climate
Ashenmarch is a dry, rocky badland region with sparse vegetation, red dust storms, and extreme heat during the day. The landscape is scarred by old demonic invasions, with ruined forts and blackened earth. Water is scarce, and most settlements are built around fortified oases or underground aquifers.
