Northeast: Borders demon territory directly (most dangerous border in Veloria).
East: Borders demon territory (the Bloodstone region is the frontline).
Southeast: Borders the Kingdom of Ironmarch (strong military alliance due to shared demon threat).
South: Borders the Grand Duchy of Dawnridge (strained relations due to resource disputes).
Southwest: Borders the Kingdom of Ravenwood (dark forests, occasional skirmishes).
West: Borders the Grand Duchy of Ironcross (mountainous, good trade relations).
Northwest: Borders the Kingdom of Stormcrown (mountainous, occasional border tensions).

Strategic Importance
Ashenmarch is one of the most critical defensive lines against demonic expansion. It suffers constant raids but serves as a buffer that protects the richer central duchies. The Grand Duke maintains one of the largest standing armies among the Grand Duchies.
